{"tid":2442801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完鍾培生channel D片 覺得佢係浪費緊成個家族嘅錢","createTime":"2021-03-11T15:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T15:35:50.000Z","uid":169275,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eb46bce97dee455f8dc690a85fe11c136c5d4920","tid":2442801,"uid":169275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWMSFAN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWMSFAN.jpg&h=e19d1d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nquote 一個留言先 呢個係佢超市無上限任掃條片嘅其中一個留言<br />\n<br />\n買成車油 以為自己好型<br />\n有無諗過人地咁多油點用得曬 而D油係咪真係適合擺咁耐？<br />\n買萬幾蚊野比個會員 學個留言話齋成舊prosciutto點食？<br />\n個會員係咪真係咁有需要<br />\n咁多錢 點解唔真係去周濟窮人同埋真係有需要嘅人？<br />\n點解人地Bill Gates多錢過佢咁多 但咁多人真係respect佢而唔係好似鐘培生咁比人話三世祖？<br />\n咁多錢但唔識善用真係可悲<br />\n<br />\n根本成個channel 搞個Derek love講到spread love咁 實際上就係幫自己賣廣告想多D人識自己 唔理做緊嘅野到底有無意義 係咪最有意義 總之吸引到眼球就做<br />\n<br />\n同林作上擂台 講到咩近年最大盛事 講到尾咪又係想seek attention？如果純碎想打 點解唔私下打？點解講到好似要全城觸目咁？比一二百萬林作 點解唔去派比窮人？<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠有錢過佢咁多 有無整個channel搞咁多野聲稱係spread love?李嘉誠基金會真係幫緊好多有需要嘅人 鐘培生又做過D咩？買一車油？買咁大舊prosciutto?"},{"pid":"d4f3ee07c9fc4cab85d9e4a7a043d4162927d7d2","tid":2442801,"uid":886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c6622214293787f7ff15f0131d58a088e359d9","tid":2442801,"uid":374180,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwUg7jB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwUg7jB.jpg&h=13cbf3d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27e55b8965814a2d4b308b695c86025a213fa78b","tid":2442801,"uid":12034,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime"